Lamborghini is the face of luxury and its driver the heart.

Lamborghini Impressions, an event that took place earlier this month, is proof. A convoy of our Huracán EVO and Huracán EVO Spyder drove along the breathtaking Malibu coast, visiting vintage and artisanal spots around California. It was an opportunity desired by many and envied by all.

#Lamborghini #HuracanEVO #HuracanEVOSpyder #EveryDayAmplified #LamborghiniImpressions

This Black Friday, get stylish with Automobili Lamborghini, and do it right now!
Explore our collection at Lamborghinistore.com.

#Lamborghini #LamborghiniStyle #BlackFriday #InformalLuxury

Look to the past to be inspired for the future. Huracàn EVO inherited its stylish good looks and distinctive lines from the classic Countach and its amazing form from the Lamborghini DNA.

#Lamborghini #HuracanEVO #Countach #CentroStileLamborghini

With strong willpower, nothing stays just a dream. @nathaliemcgloin, a proud owner of a Huracán Performante, defies societal conventions and shares her journey from public speaking at conferences to driving races in adapted Super Sports Cars.
Our visit also served as a great opportunity for her to try out our majestic Urus. She is truly inspiring!

#Lamborghini #HuracanPerformante #Urus #SinceWeMadeItPossible

Urus is the kind of Super SUV that puts its versatility to test each time it's driven and comes out a winner each time. One such conquest happens to be the Lamborghini Dinamica Terra in the mysterious and unique land of Altai Republic.

#Lamborghini #Urus #LamborghiniDinamicaTerra #SinceWeMadeItPossible

Lamborghini took exclusivity to the next level at Lamborghini Day Japan 2019 with the premiere of Aventador SVJ 63 Roadster.

The Glio Museum not only showcased this limited-edition Super Sports Car but also the three unique Japanese versions of it that were created by the teams of Centro Stile Lamborghini in collaboration with those of Ad Personam.

This event also brought together more than 200 Lamborghinis that paraded around the Osaka Castle, making for the perfect ending to this beautiful evening.

#Lamborghini #AventadorSVJ63 #HuracanEvoSpyder #LamborghiniDay

While the Urus is the modern-day equivalent of “rugged good looks”, its exterior wasn’t the only thing that was inspired by the LM 002. The fact that Centro Stile Lamborghini built the SSUV to be adaptable to all kinds of terrains is also largely based on its great predecessor. Finally, it is Lamborghini's convention-defying attitude that ties these two together.

#Lamborghini #Urus #LM002 #SinceWeMadeItPossible #CentroStileLamborghini
